OL,6,FUS Attorney for the Western District
OL,7,Fof Virginia, Christopher Kavanaugh,
OL,8,Fwhose office prosecuted the case, said
OL,9,Fafter a plea hearing at a federal
OL,10,Fcourt in Charlottesville that Envigo
OL,11,Fand Inotiv "prioritised profits and
OL,12,Fconvenience over following the law."
OL,14,FHe said the company generated $16
OL,15,Fmillion (#12.5 million) in revenue
OL,16,Fbetween 2019 and May 2022, when the
OL,17,Fsearch occurred, through the sale of
OL,18,F15,000 beagles.
